		<h2>Alexandra Merdian (guest teacher)</h2>
		<p>Alex's experience with yoga started in 2006 when her mom bought her a yoga mat and a power yoga DVD. For a long time, she practiced alone at home, and only a few years ago, she began to practice under the guidance of other yoga teachers. In 2016, Alex completed her 200-hour yoga teacher training at Yoga Akademie parApara at Lalla and Villas in Berlin. Her classes are taught in German.</p>
